  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Food Science              : The relationship between the chemistry of food constituents present in common commodities, such as milk, meat, eggs, cereals, oilseeds etc. and the common processing technologies associated with their transformation into stable food products.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
